  <script type="text/javascript">
    function recordOutboundLink(link, category, action) {
        
                  
            if(typeof(ga) != 'undefined') {
                ga('send', 'event', category, action);
            }
          
                

        if( ( action == 'link_site_agentie' || action == 'link_anunt_extern' ) &&
            typeof aTexte != "undefined" &&
            typeof aTexte.b_contact != "undefined" &&
            typeof aTexte.b_contact.sIdUnicOferta != "undefined" ){

            var id_lista = parseInt(get_params()['lista']);
            var iSursa = aTexte.b_contact.iSursa;
            if (typeof id_lista != 'undefined') {
                iSursa = iSursa + '|' + id_lista;
            }
            if( typeof aTexte.b_contact.sSursaText != 'undefined' ){
                iSursa = aTexte.b_contact.sSursaText;
            }

            $.post(aTexte.general.sPortalUrl + 'oferta/link-extern',
                    {'sIdUnicOferta' : aTexte.b_contact.sIdUnicOferta, 'iCategorie' : aTexte.b_contact.iCategorie, 'iTipTranzactie' : aTexte.b_contact.iTipTranzactie, 'iSursa' : iSursa})
        }

        if( typeof( link.href ) != 'undefined' && link.href.length ) {
            if(action == 'salveaza_anunt_add'){
              setTimeout('window.open("' + link.href + '", "_self")', 100);
            } else {
              setTimeout('window.open("' + link.href + '"' + ((action == 'link_site_agentie') ? ', "_blank"' : '') + ')', 100);
            }
        } else {
            if(action == 'salveaza_anunt_add'){
              setTimeout('window.open("' + link + '", "_self")', 100);
            } else {
              setTimeout('window.open("' + link + '"' + ((action == 'link_site_agentie') ? ', "_blank"' : '') + ')', 100);
            }
        }
    }
    function ignoreAgencyActions(action) {
        var agency = 'showEnergy';
        if (get_cookie(agency) == null) {
            return false;
        }
        var actions = ['contact_chat', 'contact_email', 'contact_telefon', 'contact_mobil_confirmat', 'contact_mobil_sms'];
        if (actions.indexOf(action) == -1) {
            return false;
        }
        
                
        return true;
    }
    function recordActionClick(target, category, action, bNonInteraction) {
        var leadAction = false,
            salveazaAutomatAnuntFavorit = false;

        switch (action) {
            case 'contact_email':
            case 'contact_telefon':
            case 'contact_email_galerie':
                leadAction = true;
                break;
            case 'contact_chat':
                leadAction = true;
                salveazaAutomatAnuntFavorit = true;
                break;
        }

        
                

        if(typeof(ga) != 'undefined' && ga.create) {
            if (!ignoreAgencyActions(action)) {
                if (category == 'action_click_imoagent') {
                    if (typeof aTexte != "undefined" && typeof aTexte.general != "undefined" && aTexte.general.iLogamEventuriAnalytics == 1) {
                        ga('send', 'event', category, action, target, {nonInteraction: typeof bNonInteraction != 'undefined'});
                    }
                } else {
                    ga('send', 'event', category, action, target, {nonInteraction: typeof bNonInteraction != 'undefined'});
                }

                if (leadAction) {
                    recordLeadAction(target, category, action);
                }
            }
        } else {
            if (leadAction) {
                recordLeadAction(target, category, action);
                trimiteLogGoogleAnalyticsBlocat(target, category, action);
            }
        }
        
                

        if (salveazaAutomatAnuntFavorit) {
            detaliiOfertaPreluareOfertaFavoritaScript();
        }
    }

    function trimiteLogGoogleAnalyticsBlocat(target, category, action) {
        if (typeof aTexte !== "undefined" &&
            typeof aTexte.general !== "undefined" &&
            typeof  aTexte.general.sPortalUrl !== "undefined"
        ) {
            $.ajax({
                type: "POST",
                dataType: "json",
                url: aTexte.general.sPortalUrl + 'logare-google-analytics-blocat',
                data: {target: target, category: category, action: action},
            });
        }
    }

    function recordLeadAction(target, category, action)
    {
        if (typeof Indicative !== "undefined") {
            Indicative.buildEvent(action, {"target": target, "category": category});
        }
    }

    function detaliiOfertaPreluareOfertaFavoritaScript() {
        var script = "";
        var isIframe = (self.frameElement && (self.frameElement+"").indexOf("HTMLIFrameElement") > -1);

        if (isIframe) {
            parent.postMessage("salveazaOfertaAutomat", location.origin);
        } else if ($("#content-detalii").length > 0) {

            if ($('.anunt_favorit').length > 0) {
                var $element = $('.anunt_favorit');
                if ($element.hasClass('salveaza')) {
                    script = $element.attr("data-click");
                    ruleazaScriptOferteFavoriteAutomat(script);
                }
            }
        }
    }

    function ruleazaScriptOferteFavoriteAutomat(script) {
        if (typeof script !== "undefined") {
            if (script.length > 0) {
                if (script.indexOf('xajax_toggleAnuntSalvat') !== -1) {
                    var rezultat = script.match(/\((.*)\)/);
                    if (typeof rezultat[1] !== "undefined") {
                        var parametrii = rezultat[1].split(",");

                        if (typeof parametrii[6] === "undefined") {
                            parametrii[6] = "''";
                        }

                        if (parametrii.length >= 7) {
                            parametrii[7] = true;

                            var newScript = "xajax_toggleAnuntSalvat(" + parametrii.join(",") + ");";

                            eval(newScript);
                        }
                    }
                }
            }
        }
    }
  </script>

                                'exp_ver': 5
                            };
                            this.profileSet('did_search', 1);
                            this.profileSet('notif_frequency', frequency);
                            if (imovzt && (!result || result != imovzt)) {
                                tags.imovzt = imovzt;
                                this.profileSet('imovzt', imovzt);
                            }
                            this.tag(tags);
                        }.bind(this));
                    }
                },
                onAlreadySubscribed: this.onSubscribed,
                promptConditions: function () {
                    return window.aTexte && window.aTexte.lista && window.aTexte.lista.idLista;
                }
            };

            (function () {
                s = document.createElement('script');
                s.type = 'text/javascript';
                s.async = true;
                s.defer = true;
                s.src = 'https://imopush.imobiliare.ro/sdk/app.js';
                document.head.appendChild(s);

                $(document).ready(function () {
                    if (typeof Movalio !== "undefined") {
                        var areCont = 0;
                        Movalio.profileGet('has_account').then(function (result) {
                            if (typeof result === "undefined" && areCont === 1) {
                                Movalio.tag('has_account', areCont);
                                Movalio.profileSet('has_account', areCont);
                            }
                        });
                    }
                });
            })();
        }

        
                

        function isSupportedBrowserForWebPush() {
            try {
                if (!('serviceWorker' in navigator)) {
                    throw new Error('No Service Worker support!');
                }
                if (!('PushManager' in window)) {
                    throw new Error('No Push API Support!');
                }
                if (!('indexedDB' in window)) {
                    throw new Error('No indexedDB Support!');
                }
                var ua = navigator.userAgent.toLowerCase();
                if (ua.indexOf('safari') != -1) {
                    if (ua.indexOf('chrome') === -1) {
                        throw new Error('It\'s Safari');
                    }
                }
            } catch (e) {
                return false;
            }
            return true;
        }

class="titlu-box">Detalii</h2> <p>THALASSA IMOBILIARE va propune un apartament situat in cea mai buna zona din Calea Bucuresti, imediat langa Rotonda si Stomatologie, o locatie recunoscuta si foarte cautata pentru avantaje si facilitati.<br />Pozitionat la etajul 3 intr-un bloc cu 4 niveluri, apartamentul are vedere bilaterala si compartimentare decomandata, fiind compus din living, trei dormitoare, bucatarie, 2 bai, holuri si balcon inchis.<br />Renovat in totalitate, beneficiaza de finisaje de calitate (parchet, gresie, faianta), tamplarie PVC cu geam termopan, instalatii electrice si sanitare inlocuite.<br />Sistem de alarma cu supraveghere, centrala termica proprie si instalatie climatizare A.C.<br />Apartamentul se vinde complet mobilat si utilat cu toata gama de electrocasnice.<br />Situatie juridica la zi, disponibilitate imediat.<br />Va propu<span id="descriere_inlocuita">...<a href="">Cite&#351;te mai mult</a></span><span id="arata_descriere" style="display:none">nem pretul de 95,000 Euro si va stam la dispozitie pentru relatii, detalii si programare la vizionari la telefon <span class=telefon_inlocuit id=telefon_inlocuit_1><a href='javascript:;'><u>vezi tot num&#259;rul</u></a></span>.<br /><br />THALASSA IMOBILIARE - Niciun loc nu-i ca ACASA !</span></p> </div> <div id="b_detalii_caracteristici" class="margin-boxes"> <h2 <script type="text/javascript">
    var ImoTiming = new TimingFrontend();
    var urlType = '';
            urlType = 'detalii';
            
    ImoTiming.setHost('https://www.imobiliare.ro/');
    ImoTiming.mark('document_head_end',iDocumentHeadEnd);
    ImoTiming.mark('document_body_end',(new Date().getTime()-iDocumentStart));
    if(urlType!='') ImoTiming.mark('url_type',urlType);

    jQuery(window).on('load', function() {
        setTimeout(function() {
            ImoTiming.mark('on_load',(new Date().getTime()-iDocumentStart));
            //single page call ox lista
            if(typeof(OXbanners) !== 'undefined' && OXbanners !== null) {

                OXbanners.loadBanners();
                ImoTiming.mark('load_opxads',(new Date().getTime()-iDocumentStart));
            }
            ImoTiming.send();
            if(window.performance && window.performance.timing) {
                    var timing = window.performance.timing;
                    var ImoTimingNew = new TimingFrontend();
                    ImoTimingNew.setHost('https://www.imobiliare.ro/');
                    if(urlType!='') ImoTimingNew.mark('url_type',urlType);
                    ImoTimingNew.mark('dns',timing.domainLookupEnd - timing.domainLookupStart);
                    ImoTimingNew.mark('connect',timing.connectEnd - timing.connectStart);
                    ImoTimingNew.mark('ttfb',timing.responseStart - timing.connectEnd);
                    ImoTimingNew.mark('html',timing.responseEnd - timing.responseStart);
                    ImoTimingNew.mark('dominteractive',timing.domInteractive - timing.domLoading);
                    ImoTimingNew.mark('domcomplete',timing.domComplete - timing.domInteractive);
                    ImoTimingNew.mark('onload',timing.loadEventEnd - timing.loadEventStart);
                    ImoTimingNew.send();
            }

            //lazy load restul
            if(typeof AsynchronousLoad == 'object') {
                AsynchronousLoad.lazyLoadPortal();

                var oImg = document.createElement('img');
                oImg.src = "https://www.imobiliare.ro/browsercache";
                document.body.appendChild(oImg);
            }
        }, 0);

        if(typeof(RtbHouse) != 'undefined' && typeof aTexte != 'undefined' && typeof aTexte.general != 'undefined' && aTexte.general.iIframeRTBHouseActiv == 1) {
            RtbHouse.generateIframe('other');

    

    
    
            
            if(typeof(aTexte) != 'undefined' && typeof(aTexte.b_contact) != 'undefined' && typeof(aTexte.b_contact.sIdUnicOferta) != 'undefined') {
                RtbHouse.generateIframe('offer', {sIdUnic: aTexte.b_contact.sIdUnicOferta});
            }
        
    
    
        }
    });
    
</script>
